    UpdateQuotaRequest

    public static final class UpdateQuotaRequest.Builder
extends Object
    Builds instances of type UpdateQuotaRequest. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.
